See README.md for full build instructions and dependency lists.

Quick install:

    git clone https://github.com/tryptophane/babeleo-plasma.git
    cd babeleo-plasma
    mkdir build && cd build
    cmake .. -DCMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX=/usr
    cmake --build .
    sudo cmake --install .

After installation, restart plasmashell or log out and back in.
